<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Global Nomads Ltd | Creating and Reinventing Apps for All!</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #1a252f;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        header p.tagline {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #1abc9c;
        }

        /* Main Content Container */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* App Portfolio Section */
        .apps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .app-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #1abc9c;
        }

        .app-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .app-card h3 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .app-card p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #bdc3c7;
        }

        .company-details {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
        }

        .company-details strong {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .contact-email {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #1abc9c;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .contact-email:hover {
            background-color: #16a085;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Global Nomads Ltd</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Creating and Reinventing Apps for All!</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="intro">
            <p>Welcome to Global Nomads Ltd. We build digital experiences and reinvent how you interact with technology everyday. Explore our current portfolio of applications below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="apps-grid">
            <a href="/autoquest/" class="app-card">
                <h3>AutoQuest App</h3>
                <p>Access the app, policies, and terms and conditions.</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/coffeenation/" class="app-card">
                <h3>Coffeenation App</h3>
                <p>Access the app, policies, and terms and conditions.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="company-details">
            <strong>Global Nomads Ltd</strong><br>
            167-169, Great Portland Street<br>
            5th Floor<br>
            London, W1W 5PF. UK.<br>
            Company Number: 13058694
        </div>
        
        <a href="mailto:info@globalnomads.co.uk" class="contact-email">info@globalnomads.co.uk</a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
